# =============================================================================

# Universal Ignore Template

# =============================================================================

# 用於 `.gitignore` / `.geminiignore` / `.claudeignore` (後兩者為 LLM 語境過濾)

# 安裝: `bash resources/config/install-ignore.sh`  (見同目錄腳本)

#

# 結構分區

# A. OS / FS metadata

# B. Editor / IDE

# C. Language toolchains — Node / JS / TS

# D. Language toolchains — Go

# E. Language toolchains — Python / Rust / JVM

# F. Build / Dist artifacts

# G. Tests / Coverage

# H. Logs / Runtime dumps

# I. Secrets / Env / Local config

# J. Lockfile noise

# K. AI assistant caches (Claude / Gemini / Aider / Copilot / Cursor)

# L. Misc (project-local noise)

# =============================================================================

# ── A. OS / File system metadata ──────────────────────────────────────────────

.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
ehthumbs.db
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
$RECYCLE.BIN/
*~

# ── B. Editor / IDE ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

.vscode/
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
.idea/
*.iml
*.swp
*.swo
*.swn
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace
.fleet/
.cursor/
.codium/
*.code-workspace
.project
.classpath
.settings/

# ── C. Node / JavaScript / TypeScript ────────────────────────────────────────

node_modules/
jspm_packages/
.npm/
.yarn/
.pnp.*
.pnpm-store/
